  <brief_title>The Efficacy and Safety of Thymosin-α1 in Patients With HBV-related ACLF.</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Trial to Evaluate Efficacy and Safety of Thymosin-α1 Administration in Patients With HBV-related Acute-on-chronic Liver Failure</official_title>
