  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A randomized controlled trial to evaluate efficacy and safety of Thymosin-α1 administration
      in patients with HBV-related Acute-on-chronic liver failure.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Hepatitis B virus (HBV)-related acute-on-chronic liver failure (ACLF) is a severe disease
      with high mortality. In this study, we intend to assess the efficacy and safety of
      Thymosin-α1 in patients with HBV-related Acute-on-chronic liver failure.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
